`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Harm
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast harm		 <victim>

 This spell, along with Cause Light, Cause Serious, and Cause Critical,
inflicts damage on the victim through the careful use of applied magical pain
energies. The higher level spells, which of course use more mana, cause more
damage to the victim.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
